'Police believe that no one else was injured during the incident and inquiries are ongoing to establish the exact circumstances around the fire.'

A number of people have been spotted leaving floral tributes at the scene this morning.

A statement from South Yorkshire Fire and Rescue Service said two crews were dispatched to the scene.

